column1: Baby Barnaby's////Wonderful breakfast experience at this cute place! I had the Migas for breakfast. Chilis
column6: served with potatoes and salsa. Delicious! My son had French toast
column7: another had pancakes with apples and pecans
column8: my husband the breakfast plate with biscuits
column11: and sausage. Everything was hot and fresh. I wish I had our server's name because he was great! Go visit this great place for breakfast! You will not be disappointed.
